OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776334011
OL,3,CRecord #8.5 million paid by water
OL,4,Ccompanies in enforcement action this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FPhilip Duffy, Chief Executive of the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency, said: "While we
OL,9,Fcontinue to prosecute and sanction the
OL,10,Fmost serious offences, Enforcement
OL,11,FUndertakings allow us to hold
OL,12,Fcompanies to account more quickly
OL,13,Fwhile ensuring money is channelled
OL,14,Fdirectly to where damage has occurred,
OL,15,Fdelivering real benefits for people
OL,16,Fand wildlife."
OL,26,@pD@[OUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
