OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776334011
OL,3,CRecord #8.5 million paid by water
OL,4,Ccompanies in enforcement action this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FMark Lloyd, Chief Executive of The
OL,8,FRivers Trust, said: "We would prefer
OL,9,Fthat pollution events didn't happen in
OL,10,Fthe first place and continue to push
OL,11,Ffor the necessary action to ensure
OL,12,Fthis ` including ambitious reform of
OL,13,Fthe water system.
OL,26,@pD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
