OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776334011
OL,3,CRecord #8.5 million paid by water
OL,4,Ccompanies in enforcement action this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"When pollution incidents do occur, it
OL,8,Fis right that polluters contribute to
OL,9,Fthe costs of caring for the rivers
OL,10,Fharmed by this. Enforcement
OL,11,FUndertakings are one way of
OL,12,Fchannelling vital funds into this
OL,13,Fcrucial work, but this is only a
OL,14,Ffraction of the investment needed to
OL,15,Fbuild catchment resilience to
OL,16,Fpollution, floods and drought."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
